:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係學校後樓梯屌女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDetails <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08687263adbfe360ade5857c3e18f0a77cf84025","tid":361282,"uid":41080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未試過響中學時期同學生妹發生初戀, 之後再害害羞羞咁互相獻出第一次, 真係一個永不磨滅既人生遺憾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人生無憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ce1e5256bc404c951ee5dd06c4e780448b9b02","tid":361282,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T09:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係學校後樓梯屌女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDetails <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年中學有條走火樓梯唔俾學生行，但俾老師行。教員室就係學校一樓，圖書館同多用途室係六、七樓。換句話講老師唔會行二至七樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以一定冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLunch time 果陣借D依話同佢上圖書館行呢邊快少少，上到四五樓就摷佢埋牙。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做完個套拋左出後樓梯窗口（下面係老師停車場）<br />\n人生無憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c77b2c134d6d80be2fdcfeb9551f31eae6c9c0","tid":361282,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係學校後樓梯屌女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDetails <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年中學有條走火樓梯唔俾學生行，但俾老師行。教員室就係學校一樓，圖書館同多用途室係六、七樓。換句話講老師唔會行二至<del>七樓</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以一定冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLunch time 果陣借D依話同佢上圖書館行呢邊快少少，上到四五樓就摷佢埋牙。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做完個套拋左出後樓梯窗口（下面係老師停車場）<br />\n人生無憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n五樓"},{"pid":"d5c5ae2c1e8fbcd780801af7b025e4e0e76a0812","tid":361282,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T09:42:17.000Z","msg":"比mk仔恰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253244ee8a9e9c170f68fa90bb0d05b8b36cafad","tid":361282,"uid":67010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蘋果綠茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好懷念中學既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中學食沙爹牛肉麵同三文治"},{"pid":"6d73040e9c4c99a0a412dfc64c95bd1eb21ff0ec","tid":361282,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:48:08.000Z","msg":"雞髀"},{"pid":"e319806966e0905993123562a664e9b13ac344c3","tid":361282,"uid":41080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蘋果綠茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好懷念中學既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中學食沙爹牛肉麵同三文治</blockquote><br />\n出黎做野就鐘意食"},{"pid":"daab733676f8b6516b04b4768d66265cbd94317e","tid":361282,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"玩黑板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上堂對打psp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef4cabbebf31baaa4f4581cc5a4d55d14e2bcfc","tid":361282,"uid":69090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:20:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55f2c6512c